New Horizons Kuiper Belt Flyby Object Officially Named 'Arrokoth'
In a fitting tribute to the farthest flyby ever conducted by spacecraft, the Kuiper Belt object 2014 MU69 has been officially named Arrokoth, a Native American term meaning “sky” in the Powhatan/Al...
